---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What size sauna is good for two people?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "A 2-person sauna typically measures around 4x4 feet interior. For couples who want to sit comfortably side by side with room to move, a 4-person barrel sauna (used by two) is actually a better experience — it allows one person to lie down while the other sits, which is the most comfortable way to use a sauna for extended sessions."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is a good outdoor sauna for couples?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "The Almost Heaven Pinnacle 4-Person Barrel Sauna is the most popular choice for couples — it's sized right for two people with room to stretch out, built with Canadian red cedar, and comes in at a reasonable price for the quality. For indoor use, the Dynamic Saunas Barcelona provides a full 1-2 person infrared experience."
      }
    }
  ]
};
---
<Base
  title="Best Sauna for Two People (2025): Outdoor and Indoor Picks for Couples"
  description="The best saunas for couples and two-person use. What size you actually need, outdoor barrel vs indoor infrared, and top picks at every budget."
  canonical="/guides/sauna-for-couples"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />

  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-3">Best Sauna for Two People (2025)</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-500 mb-8">Updated March 2025 &mdash; Backyard Sauna Pro</p>

    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-5 mb-8 text-sm text-stone-700">
      <strong>Affiliate disclosure:</strong> As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This page contains affiliate links.
    </div>

    <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 mb-4">Most couples buying a sauna go for a 2-person model and discover it's tighter than they expected. Two adults sitting side-by-side in a 4x4 foot interior with the heater taking up a corner is functional but not luxurious. If you're using the sauna regularly as a couple, sizing up pays off.</p>

    <p class="text-stone-700 mb-8">Here's what actually works for two people, and what to buy.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-10 mb-4">The Size Question</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">A labeled "2-person" sauna holds two people in the way a compact car holds five — technically true, less comfortable in practice. The interior is typically 36-42 inches wide. Two adults shoulder-to-shoulder with a heater in the corner works, but you can't move much.</p>
    <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">The sweet spot for a couple who plans to sauna regularly is a 4-person barrel sauna used by two. You have enough room for one person to sit and one to lie down on the bench — the ideal position for a long session. Heat-up time and electricity costs increase only slightly with the larger interior.</p>
    <p class="text-stone-700 mb-6">The only reason to choose a true 2-person is space constraints. If your yard or room can only fit a small unit, a 2-person works fine — it's just snug.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-10 mb-6">Top Picks for Couples</h2>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">

      <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-5 bg-white">
        <div class="mb-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-700 bg-amber-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide">Best Outdoor Pick</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-1">Almost Heaven Pinnacle 4-Person Barrel Sauna</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-stone-600 mb-3">The most popular barrel sauna in its price range, and the right size for two people who want real comfort. Five-foot diameter barrel in Canadian red cedar. Two people sit with plenty of room, or one person lies flat while the other sits. Heats to 185°F in about 45 minutes with a proper heater.</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-stone-600 mb-4">
          <span class="text-green-700 font-medium">Pros: right size for two, cedar quality, proven brand</span>
          <span class="mx-2">|</span>
          <span class="text-red-700 font-medium">Cons: needs 240V electrical, heater upgrade recommended</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B017WJV8SO?tag=backyardsauna-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm">Check Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-5 bg-white">
        <div class="mb-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-stone-600 bg-stone-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide">Best Indoor Pick</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-1">Dynamic Saunas Barcelona 1-2 Person</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-stone-600 mb-3">The top-rated plug-in infrared sauna for smaller spaces. Canadian hemlock, 6 low-EMF carbon heating panels, Bluetooth audio, chromotherapy light. Plugs into a standard 120V outlet — no electrician needed. Works in apartments, spare bedrooms, or basements. Two people fit comfortably seated.</p>
        <div class="text-sm text-stone-600 mb-4">
          <span class="text-green-700 font-medium">Pros: plug-in 120V, no installation, moves with you</span>
          <span class="mx-2">|</span>
          <span class="text-red-700 font-medium">Cons: max 140°F infrared, not traditional heat</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00A2F99F0?tag=backyardsauna-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm">Check Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-10 mb-4">Outdoor vs Indoor for Couples</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">If you have outdoor space and the budget for electrical work, outdoor barrel is the better long-term buy. The experience — real heat, steam, stepping out into fresh air — is genuinely different from an indoor infrared unit. It becomes a ritual you build your evenings around rather than a wellness appliance you use sometimes.</p>
    <p class="text-stone-700 mb-6">If you're in an apartment, renting, or don't want to deal with outdoor installation, the Barcelona-style plug-in infrared is a solid practical choice. You use it more consistently because there's no friction — just turn it on.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-10 mb-4">Making the Most of It as a Couple</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">The sauna-as-couple-activity works because heat lowers defenses and slows everything down. Phones stay outside, there's nowhere to go, and the conversation that happens in a sauna is often different from anywhere else. It's worth being deliberate about building the ritual — same time each week, cold plunge or cold shower after, maybe a drink or meal after the cool-down. The structure matters as much as the heat itself.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-10 mb-4">FAQ</h2>
    <div class="space-y-5">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">What size sauna is good for two people?</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-700">A 4-person barrel sauna used by two is the ideal size — enough room to sit and lie down comfortably. True 2-person saunas are functional but snug.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-1">What is a good outdoor sauna for couples?</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-700">Almost Heaven Pinnacle (outdoor barrel) for traditional heat. Dynamic Saunas Barcelona (indoor infrared) for plug-in convenience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-6 mt-10">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Related</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/guides/best-2-person-outdoor-sauna" class="text-amber-700 hover:underline">Best 2-Person Outdoor Sauna Kits</a></li>
        <li><a href="/reviews/almost-heaven-pinnacle-review" class="text-amber-700 hover:underline">Almost Heaven Pinnacle Full Review</a></li>
        <li><a href="/reviews/dynamic-saunas-barcelona-review" class="text-amber-700 hover:underline">Dynamic Saunas Barcelona Review</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/sauna-cold-plunge" class="text-amber-700 hover:underline">Sauna and Cold Plunge Guide</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </article>
</Base>
